Package: kootnet-network-testers
Version: 1.2-4
Section: utils
Priority: extra
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-venv, bash, wget, mtr, iperf3
Recommends: fonts-freefont-ttf, fake-hwclock
Maintainer: Chad Ermacora <chad.e@linux.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/chad-ermacora/rp-network-testers
Description: Kootnet Network Testers
 Turn 2x Raspberry Pis (and some other GNU/Linux computers) into Network Testers
 Runs MTR & iPerf3 to test latency & throughput on individual cables or network routes.
